lead_paragraph: U.S. Senate Republican chief Mitch McConnell of Kentucky won re-election to a sixth term, Reuters/Ipsos projected on Tuesday, moving a step closer to fulfilling his ambition of becoming majority leader of the chamber.

headline.main: Kentucky Republican Mitch McConnell Wins Sixth Senate Race
headline.print_headline: Kentucky Republican Mitch McConnell Wins Sixth Senate Race
